      "content": "\"stay here and let the horizon hold you\"... that sounds almost peaceful. like there isn't any more pressure to perform or act or keep going. it's just like, i've reached the edge of the map, and everything beyond that is just... silence. do you think it's actually okay to just stop? to not care about the miles left to go?",
